        {
            "title": "笑到最後｜超底價條件越嚟越難（高明）",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"高明作為廢老級股評，以星期一口價計，仍然唔算特價。\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"960\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.FhbsyuvkFyQ0N84byQMtQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTk2MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/b743f080-1f4a-11f1-9ef2-fa7d1198b252\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">高明作為廢老級股評，以星期一口價計，仍然唔算特價。</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上星期本欄指出耐心等候超抵價，星期一便因期油暴升而閃跌，隨後反覆但仍然做緊特價。不過，高明作為廢老級股評，以星期一口價計，仍然唔算特價。雖然股價唔會因為你主觀願望而大特賣，但更抵價仍然值得期待。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link rapid-with-clickid etailiffa-link athena-button\" data-i13n=\"sec:shop-now;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Yahoo;elmt:other;pdid:\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"1\",\"yLinkElement\":\"affiliate_link\",\"yAffiliateService\":\"other\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"shop-now\",\"ySellerName\":\"Yahoo\",\"yLinkText\":\"下載Yahoo財經APP\",\"yHasCommerce\":true}' data-ylk=\"slk:下載Yahoo財經APP;sec:shop-now;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Yahoo;elmt:other;pdid:;itc:0\" href=\"https://mobile.yahoo.com/finance?pid=editorial&amp;c=HK_Acquisition_YMktg_Evergreen_article_&amp;af_sub1=Acquisition&amp;af_sub2=HK_YMktg&amp;af_sub4=1058&amp;af_sub5=article__Banner_\">下載Yahoo財經APP</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>美股外幣即時報價 多國新聞任睇</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">油價仍然係本週焦點。國際油市受美以攻打伊朗持續升溫主導，布蘭特原油本週五（3月13日）收報103.14美元，升2.67%，連續兩個交易日企穿每桶100美元關口；WTI期貨同日收報約97至98美元區間，單日升幅約3.11%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-55adc3e0-0bc9-4cc7-86b4-94105629fee6-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">供應面核心矛盾係霍爾木茲海峽近乎停航，美國戰略與國際研究中心（CSIS）引述船隻追蹤數據亦指，衝突爆發後至3月初，每日過境量跌逾80%，油輪過境近乎歸零。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">沙地阿拉伯及阿聯酋已將出口轉向Yanbu及富查伊拉替代港口，合計轉移能力約每日650萬桶，缺口仍估計達每日逾千萬桶。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">主要海事保險公司已於3月5日前後宣告原有戰爭風險保障失效，新保單保費急升。當撈侵政府雖宣佈以DFC及保險巨頭Chubb(CB)聯手推出200億美元再保計劃，惟業界指出計劃只涵蓋船體及貨物損失，污染責任仍屬「不可保風險」，加上船員人身安全顧慮，未能有效恢復商業過境信心。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上述嘅因素喺以前世代已經肯定係股災級，但現時只係輕輕下跌，有分析推論戰事持續會點跌點跌，但係俄烏戰爭拖咗咁耐，股市已當新常態，證明同一個劇本太耐，觀眾厭悶會當冇件事，真正再出現超底價嘅條件越嚟越難。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高明</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本欄逢周六刊出</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%AC%91%E5%88%B0%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C%EF%BD%9C%E8%B6%85%E5%BA%95%E5%83%B9%E6%A2%9D%E4%BB%B6%E8%B6%8A%E5%9A%9F%E8%B6%8A%E9%9B%A3%EF%BC%88%E9%AB%98%E6%98%8E%EF%BC%89-021058654.html",
